name: libosmscout
short_description: libosmscout offers applications simple, high-level interfaces to offline rendering and routing functionalities based on OpenStreetMap data. It does so by preprocessing *.osm data files and generating binary data and index files for fast access.
summary: Library for OpenStreetMap offline rendering and routing
